review_blob: This unusual beer has a very strong initial smoke flavor that mellowed slightly, but not enough, leaving a very unremarkable beer. glad i tried it but cant recommend. Just too strong smoke. Maybe with a breakfast burrito next time? If there is one.
beer_name: Rogue Voodoo Doughnut Bacon Maple Ale

review_blob: this hoppy brew from victory pours a full tan head over a nice clear orange liquor. Slight alcohol aroma wiith a strong hop bitterness. A medium bodied ale with a long bitter finish. i like this beer, its nice and strong, very hoppy and sweet. A perfect beer to have at the end of the night to unwind.
